매장위치 지도에 표시¶

In [32]:
m = folium.Map([lat,long],zoom_start = 12,tiles='Stamen Toner')

for i in df_hamburger.index:
    sub_lat = df_hamburger.loc[i,'']
    sub_long = df_hamburger.loc[i,'']
    name = df_hamburger.loc[i,'']
    address = df_hamburger.loc[i,'']
    
    icon_color = 'red'
    
    if df_hamburger.loc[i,''] == '':
        icon_color = 'purple'
    elif df_hamburger.loc[i,''] == '':
        icon_color = 'brown'
    elif df_hamburger.loc[i,''] == '':
        icon_color='orange'
        
    elif df_hamburger.loc[i,''] == 'kfc':
        icon_color = 'pink'
    
    folium.CircleMarker([sub_lat,sub_long],
                       tooltip=f'{name} - {address}',
                        radius = 3,
                        fill=True,
                       color = icon_color
                       ).add_to(m)
        
    
m

In [38]:
m = folium.Map([lat,long],zoom_start = 12,tiles='Stamen Toner')

for i in df_ham_pivot.index:
    sub_lat = df_ham_pivot.loc[i,'']
    sub_long = df_ham_pivot.loc[i,'']
    hamburgers = ['','','','','kfc']
    
    for hamburger in hamburgers:

        ham_count = df_ham_pivot.loc[i,hamburger]
        radius_ham = np.sqrt(ham_count) * 3
        name =f'{hamburger} : {ham_count}'
            
        icon_color = 'red'
        
        if hamburger == '':
            icon_color = 'purple'
            sub_lat = sub_lat + 0.005
            
        elif hamburger == '':
            icon_color = 'brown'
            sub_lat = sub_lat - 0.005
            
        elif hamburger == '':
            icon_color='orange'
            sub_long = sub_long + 0.005
            sub_lat = sub_lat + 0.005
            
            
        elif hamburger == 'kfc':
            icon_color = 'pink'
            sub_long = sub_long - 0.005
            sub_lat = sub_lat - 0.005
            
            

        folium.CircleMarker([sub_lat,sub_long],
                       tooltip=name,
                        radius = radius_ham,
                        fill=True,
                       color = icon_color
                       ).add_to(m)

    
m
